    <p class="description">A three-step data integration process that pulls raw data from source systems, cleans and restructures it, then loads it into a warehouse for unified reporting. The <strong>global ETL market reached $15 billion in 2024</strong> — powering cross-channel marketing dashboards and attribution models.</p>
